data.description: Former Lifestyle Homes model in Chimney Lakes with Mother-In-Law Suite! This home boasts tons of extras including a true Mother-In-Law Suite with its own exterior entry/exit that makes it perfect for a multi-generational family or rental income! The main living area has 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, kitchen living room, dining room and a breakfast nook with bay window. You will also find a large Florida room located off of the living room. Plenty of room in the backyard to add a private pool! Other features include a fireplace, irrigation and hurricane shutters. Large Corner Lot!
